text: Srinivas Rangaraj (15 August 1932 - 2 February 2010) was an Indian cricketer who played in sixteen first-class matches for Mysore between 1952 and 1961. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1932 births Category:2010 deaths Category:Indian cricketers Category:Karnataka cricketers Category:Place of birth missing
title: Srinivas Rangaraj
